---
// GTM Problem Section - Fear + Agitation (Daytona-style)
// Make the problem visceral and urgent
---

<section class="problem">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-label">The Problem</div>
    <h2>AI Can Write Dangerous Commands.<br />And You'll Run Them.</h2>

    <div class="problem-grid">
      <div class="problem-card danger">
        <div class="problem-icon">üíÄ</div>
        <h3>The AI Hallucination</h3>
        <p>ChatGPT doesn't validate commands. It generates what looks right‚Äîeven if it deletes your entire filesystem.</p>
        <div class="code-example">
          <code>rm -rf / --no-preserve-root</code>
          <span class="code-label">‚Üê GPT-4 actually generated this</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card warning">
        <div class="problem-icon">‚òÅÔ∏è</div>
        <h3>The Privacy Leak</h3>
        <p>Every command you type reveals your infrastructure. Server names. File paths. API keys. All sent to the cloud.</p>
        <div class="stat-callout">
          <span class="stat-number">$4.4M</span>
          <span class="stat-text">Average cost of a data breach (IBM, 2024)</span>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card warning">
        <div class="problem-icon">üîß</div>
        <h3>The Platform Trap</h3>
        <p>Works on Mac. Breaks on Linux. BSD vs GNU. sed vs gsed. You won't know until production is down.</p>
        <div class="code-example subtle">
          <code>sed -i '' 's/old/new/' # Mac</code>
          <code>sed -i 's/old/new/'    # Linux</code>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="problem-card danger">
        <div class="problem-icon">‚è∞</div>
        <h3>The 2 AM Mistake</h3>
        <p>Tired. On-call. Incident happening. One wrong keystroke between "fix deployed" and "career over."</p>
        <div class="quote-callout">
          "I've seen a senior engineer accidentally nuke prod with a misplaced space."
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="problem-summary">
      <p>Every other AI tool generates commands and hopes you check them.</p>
      <p class="highlight">What if your tool checked them for you?</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .problem {
    padding: 100px 24px;
    background: var(--color-bg-secondary);
  }

  .container {
    max-width: 1100px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-label {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 2px;
    color: #ef4444;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  h2 {
    text-align: center;
    font-size: 42px;
    font-weight: 800;
    line-height: 1.2;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .problem-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
    gap: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 60px;
  }

  .problem-card {
    background: var(--color-bg);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: border-color 0.2s, transform 0.2s;
  }

  .problem-card:hover {
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .problem-card.danger {
    border-left: 4px solid #ef4444;
  }

  .problem-card.warning {
    border-left: 4px solid #f59e0b;
  }

  .problem-icon {
    font-size: 40px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .problem-card h3 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .problem-card p {
    font-size: 16px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .code-example {
    background: #1a1a2e;
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    font-family: 'SF Mono', 'Monaco', 'Fira Code', monospace;
    font-size: 13px;
  }

  .code-example code {
    display: block;
    color: #ef4444;
  }

  .code-example.subtle code {
    color: #f59e0b;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .code-example.subtle code:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .code-label {
    display: block;
    margin-top: 8px;
    font-size: 12px;
    color: #666;
    font-family: system-ui, sans-serif;
  }

  .stat-callout {
    background: rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.1);
    border: 1px solid rgba(245, 158, 11, 0.2);
    border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 16px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .stat-number {
    display: block;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: #f59e0b;
  }

  .stat-text {
    font-size: 13px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
  }

  .quote-callout {
    font-style: italic;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    padding-left: 16px;
    border-left: 2px solid var(--color-border);
    font-size: 15px;
  }

  .problem-summary {
    text-align: center;
    max-width: 600px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .problem-summary p {
    font-size: 20px;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .problem-summary .highlight {
    font-size: 24px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    h2 {
      font-size: 28px;
    }

    .problem-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }

    .problem-card {
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .problem-summary p {
      font-size: 17px;
    }

    .problem-summary .highlight {
      font-size: 20px;
    }
  }
</style>
